{
  "id": "medicine-fate",
  "title": "药缘",
  "author": "深深",
  "cover": "/assets/images/covers/medicine-fate.jpg",
  "description": "魔教覆灭后，药修女主沈当归在地窖中捡到了一个被下了二十七种毒的药人。一段关于研究与救赎的故事就此展开。",
  "tags": [
    "古风",
    "玄幻",
    "药修",
    "救赎",
    "GB"
  ],
  "status": "Incomplete",
  "likes": 0,
  "characters": [
    {
      "id": "protagonist",
      "name": "沈当归（我）",
      "isDiscovered": true,
      "role": "药修女主",
      "avatar": "/assets/images/avatars/shen-dangui.jpg",
      "persona": "冷静、专注、坦荡",
      "background": "三百岁的药修，专攻毒理，在魔教覆灭后在地窖中捡到了药人念恩。",
      "hearts": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "nian-en",
      "name": "念恩",
      "isDiscovered": true,
      "role": "药人男主",
      "avatar": "/assets/images/avatars/nian-en.jpg",
      "persona": "温顺、敏感、知恩图报",
      "background": "被魔教下了二十七种毒的药人，编号十九，后被沈当归收养。",
      "hearts": 0
    }
  ],
  "chapters": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "地窖",
      "initialMessage": "魔教覆灭那天，沈当归去废墟里翻捡东西...",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "p1-1",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "魔教覆灭那天，我去废墟里翻捡东西。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我是药修，专攻毒理。魔教炼丹房常有残存典籍、未用灵药，都是好东西。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "翻到一半，我听见地下有声音。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1_p1_investigate",
              "text": "循声找去",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p1-2"]
            },
            {
              "id": "c1_p1_continue",
              "text": "继续翻找",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p1-3"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p1-2",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "循声找去，发现一处隐蔽的地窖入口。掀开石板，一股腥腐之气扑面而来。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "地窖角落里蹲着一个人，身上缠着锁链，听见动静，本能地往后缩。"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/assets/images/medicine-fate/nianen_ch1_cell.jpg",
              "description": "地窖中被锁链束缚的念恩"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "她走过去，蹲下，扣住他的手腕。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "二十七种毒。相生相克，相互制衡，层层叠加，竟在他体内形成一个精妙的平衡。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "她活了三百岁，第一次见到如此完美的'活毒经'。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1_p2_ask",
              "text": "询问他的名字",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p1-4"]
            },
            {
              "id": "c1_p2_leave",
              "text": "转身离开",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p1-5"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p1-3",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "她继续翻找，找到了几本炼丹典籍和一些珍贵药材。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "但她始终放不下那个声音，最终还是决定去看看。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1_p3_investigate",
              "text": "循声找去",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p1-2"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p1-4",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "你叫什么？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "……十九。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "那是编号。我叫沈当归。跟我走。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "为什么？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "你身上这二十七种毒，我想研究。每日看，慢慢看，看到你看不动为止。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1_p4_wait",
              "text": "等待他的回答",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p1-6"]
            },
            {
              "id": "c1_p4_press",
              "text": "催促他",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p1-6"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p1-5",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "她转身离开，却走了几步又停下。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "那个被锁链束缚的身影一直在她脑海里挥之不去。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1_p5_return",
              "text": "返回地窖",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p1-2"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p1-6",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他沉默了很久。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "你……研究完了会怎样？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "不知道。总之你死之前，我都会养着你。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他看着她。那眼睛很干净，没有恶意，没有怜悯——就是坦坦荡荡的'我想要'。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "好。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "你答应了？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "嗯。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "有些可能会疼。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "我疼惯了。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1_p6_next",
              "text": "进入第二章",
              "action": "redirect",
              "url": "https://app.kiragb.com/?novel=medicine-fate#chapter-2",
              "nextParagraphs": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "extendedParagraphs": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "当归",
      "initialMessage": "她把他带回山中洞府，安置在偏室...",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "p2-1",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我把他带回山中洞府，安置在偏室。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "第二天，我打了热水，拿了干净衣服，放在他门口。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他洗完，站在院子里晒太阳——六年来第一次。"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/assets/images/medicine-fate/nianen_ch2_sunshine.jpg",
              "description": "念恩在院子里晒太阳"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我出来，走过去，扣住他的手腕，开始把脉。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c2_p1_check",
              "text": "检查他的伤势",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p2-2"]
            },
            {
              "id": "c2_p1_ignore",
              "text": "直接开始研究",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p2-3"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p2-2",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "疼吗？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "不疼。早没知觉了。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "知觉没了，不是好事。以后我每日给你行针，慢慢养回来。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "你……要给我治？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "不然怎么看？你死了我看谁？"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c2_p2_cook",
              "text": "去做饭",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p2-4"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p2-3",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我开始记录他体内的毒素情况，专注地研究着。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "直到傍晚，我才想起他需要吃饭。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c2_p3_cook",
              "text": "去做饭",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p2-4"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p2-4",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "那天晚上，我做了饭。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我平时辟谷，但他要吃。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我端出一碗黑乎乎的东西，放在他面前。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "好吃。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他没说的是——那是他这辈子第一次吃到专门为他做的饭。"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/assets/images/medicine-fate/nianen_ch2_eating.jpg",
              "description": "念恩第一次吃饭的样子"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他默念我的名字：沈当归。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他记住了。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c2_p4_next",
              "text": "进入第三章",
              "action": "redirect",
              "url": "https://app.kiragb.com/?novel=medicine-fate#chapter-3",
              "nextParagraphs": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "extendedParagraphs": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "念恩",
      "initialMessage": "她开始每日记录他的毒情...",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "p3-1",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我开始每日记录他的毒情。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "有一天，我递给他一枚玉简：'注入神识，就能看见我写的。'"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他注入神识，眼前出现密密麻麻的字：十九号，约二十二岁，体内含二十七种毒……"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c3_p1_ask",
              "text": "询问十九号的称呼",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p3-2"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p3-2",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "十九号？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "不知你叫什么。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "我叫念恩。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "念恩？谁起的？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "师父。以前的师父。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我没问，只是把玉简拿回去，刻了一行字：念恩，约二十二岁。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "然后递给他。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他注入神识，看见那行字。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "念恩。不是十九号。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他把玉简握在手里，很久没说话。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c3_p2_next",
              "text": "进入第四章",
              "action": "redirect",
              "url": "https://app.kiragb.com/?novel=medicine-fate#chapter-4",
              "nextParagraphs": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "extendedParagraphs": []
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "姜附汤",
      "initialMessage": "冬天来了。他怕冷——药人的身体，阳气亏损...",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "p4-1",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "冬天来了。他怕冷——药人的身体，阳气亏损。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我发现他夜里睡不着，蜷在被子里发抖。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "第二天，我熬了一锅汤，端给他。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "喝了。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他喝了一口，暖的，微微发辣。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c4_p1_ask",
              "text": "询问汤的名字",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p4-2"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p4-2",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "这是什么？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "姜附汤。驱寒的。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他一口气喝完，果然暖和了些。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "第二天，他发现门口多了一个暖炉。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他抱着暖炉，坐在院子里晒太阳。"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/assets/images/medicine-fate/nianen_ch4_warming.jpg",
              "description": "念恩抱着暖炉晒太阳"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我出来，伸手探了探他的手。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "手还凉。明天再加一味药。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c4_p2_ask",
              "text": "询问为什么对他好",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p4-3"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p4-3",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "你为什么对我这么好？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "不是对你好。是怕你冻死了没人给我研究。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "哦。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我转身走了。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他抱着暖炉，看着我的背影。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "以前在魔教，那些人研究他，是从不管他冷不冷的。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c4_p3_next",
              "text": "进入第五章",
              "action": "redirect",
              "url": "https://app.kiragb.com/?novel=medicine-fate#chapter-5",
              "nextParagraphs": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "extendedParagraphs": []
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "阿姊",
      "initialMessage": "有一天，我在丹房炼丹，他在旁边帮忙递药材...",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "p5-1",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "有一天，我在丹房炼丹，他在旁边帮忙递药材。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "阿姊。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我手顿了顿，回头。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他脸有点红，手里捧着一把当归。"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/assets/images/medicine-fate/nianen_ch5_blushing.jpg",
              "description": "念恩捧着当归，脸红红的"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "为什么叫阿姊？"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他低着头，不说话。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c5_p1_ask",
              "text": "追问原因",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p5-2"]
            },
            {
              "id": "c5_p1_ignore",
              "text": "继续炼丹",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p5-3"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p5-2",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "为什么不说话？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "我...不知道该怎么叫你。'沈前辈'太生分，'当归'又觉得不合适。'阿姊'好像刚刚好——不是特别亲近，但也不生分。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我沉默了一会儿，继续炼丹。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "那天晚上，我在丹房里，忽然想起那个称呼。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我也不知道为什么，但那个称呼，听起来……不讨厌。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c5_p2_next",
              "text": "进入第六章",
              "action": "redirect",
              "url": "https://app.kiragb.com/?novel=medicine-fate#chapter-6",
              "nextParagraphs": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p5-3",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我没说不让叫。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "那就是可以叫吧？"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "那天晚上，我在丹房里，忽然想起那个称呼。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我也不知道为什么，但那个称呼，听起来……不讨厌。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c5_p3_next",
              "text": "进入第六章",
              "action": "redirect",
