    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "茶",
      "initialMessage": "我喜欢喝茶，早上起来必泡一壶...",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "p7-1",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我喜欢喝茶，早上起来必泡一壶。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "有一天早上，我起来，发现茶已经泡好了，放在我常坐的石桌旁。温度刚好，飘着淡淡的茶香。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我看向院子里，他正在晒药材，竹筛里铺着刚采的黄芩，阳光洒在他发梢，像是镀了一层金。"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/assets/images/medicine-fate/nianen_ch7_making_tea.jpg",
              "description": "念恩在院子里晒药材"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c7_p1_ask",
              "text": "询问茶的事",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p7-2"]
            },
            {
              "id": "c7_p1_silent",
              "text": "默默喝茶",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p7-3"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p7-2",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "第二天早上，茶又泡好了，温度依然刚好。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "第三天，第四天……连续七天，每天清晨石桌上都有一杯温度适宜的茶。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "第七天，我端着茶杯走到他身边，问：'你怎么知道我喜欢这个温度？'"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "前几天看你喝茶时，第一天皱了皱眉，第二天吹了半天，第三天你喝的时候没什么表情..."
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "所以你试了七天？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "嗯..."
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c7_p2_response",
              "text": "回应他",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p7-4"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p7-3",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我端起茶杯，轻轻抿了一口。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "茶的温度刚刚好，入口温润，回甘悠长。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我看向院子里的他，他似乎察觉到我的目光，抬头冲我笑了笑，阳光在他眼底跳跃。"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/assets/images/medicine-fate/nianen_ch7_smiling.jpg",
              "description": "念恩冲我微笑"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c7_p3_next",
              "text": "进入第八章",
              "action": "redirect",
              "url": "https://app.kiragb.com/?novel=medicine-fate#chapter-8",
              "nextParagraphs": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p7-4",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我把茶喝完，站起来，走到他面前。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "以后不用试了。现在这个温度，刚好。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他抬头看我，眼睛亮得像星子。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我已经转身回丹房。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他站在那，愣了一会儿，嘴角慢慢弯起来。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c7_p4_next",
              "text": "进入第八章",
              "action": "redirect",
              "url": "https://app.kiragb.com/?novel=medicine-fate#chapter-8",
              "nextParagraphs": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "extendedParagraphs": []
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "灯",
      "initialMessage": "他怕黑...",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "p8-1",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他怕黑。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "有一天晚上，我经过他门口，听见里面传来压抑的喘息声。我推开门，看见他蜷在床上，浑身发抖。"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/assets/images/medicine-fate/nianen_ch8_scared.jpg",
              "description": "念恩在黑暗中发抖"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我走过去，坐在床边。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "阿姊..."
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c8_p1_comfort",
              "text": "安慰他",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p8-2"]
            },
            {
              "id": "c8_p1_stay",
              "text": "默默陪伴",
              "nextParagraphs": ["p8-3"]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "p8-2",
          "parts": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "做噩梦？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "嗯...梦到以前在魔教的日子..."
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我没说话，只是轻轻拍了拍他的背。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "过了很久，他平静下来。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "我站起来，往外走。走到门口，我回头：'明天给你做盏灯。'"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "第二天，他屋里多了一盏灵玉灯，不用添油，自己会亮，光温温润润的。"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "念恩",
              "text": "这是..."
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "沈当归（我）",
              "text": "晚上起夜用的。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "他愣了一下。他起夜？他从不起夜。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "但我已经走了。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "那天晚上，他看着那盏灯，亮了一夜。"
            },
            {
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "有光在，好像真的没那么怕了。"
            }
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c8_p2_next",
              "text": "进入下一章",
              "action": "redirect",
              "url": "https://app.kiragb.com/?novel=medicine-fate#chapter-9",
              "nextParagraphs": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
